      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-08/biden-bets-fed-will-cut-rates-soon-as-he-pledges-housing-help</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登预测美联储将很快降息，因为政府在与唐纳德·特朗普的竞选斗争中更加重视住房成本。]]></description>
